== 反響 ==
《異種獵殺》獲得差評居多。在[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]上根據14則評論，電影新鮮度僅21%，平均得分為3.3／10。<ref>{{cite web |title= Breach (2020) |url= https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/breach_2020 |website= [[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |access-date= 2021-02-03 |archive-date= 2021-04-24 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210424051731/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/breach_2020 |dead-url= no }}</ref>{{le|JoBlo.com|JoBlo.com}}從滿分10分中給該片6分：「這適合作為非常特定子類型的電影，能在正確的思維下執行。這是部廉價的太空恐怖片，夠聰明將一些非常討人喜歡且具有超凡魅力的演員做主打。」<ref>{{cite web|author=The Iceman|title=BREACH (2020), RACHEL NICHOLS, BRUCE WILLIS, (HORROR MOVIE REVIEW)|publisher=[[JoBlo.com|JoBlo.com]]|url=https://www.joblo.com/horror-movies/news/breach-2020-rachel-nichols-bruce-willis-horror-movie-review|access-date=2020-12-18|archive-date=2021-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121234311/https://www.joblo.com/horror-movies/news/breach-2020-rachel-nichols-bruce-willis-horror-movie-review|dead-url=no}}</ref>

布魯斯·威利以該片連同《[[綁票追殺令|綁票追殺令]]》和《[[惡夜救援|惡夜救援]]》入圍{{le|金酸莓獎最差男配角|Golden Raspberry Award for Worst Supporting Actor}}。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/movies/movie-news/razzies-nominations-dolittle-sia-music-365-days-2021-1140766|title='Dolittle,' Sia's 'Music,' '365 Days' Lead 2021 Razzie Awards Nominees|website=[[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]]|last=Kreps|first=Daniel|date=2021-03-12|access-date=2021-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210312190325/https://www.rollingstone.com/movies/movie-news/razzies-nominations-dolittle-sia-music-365-days-2021-1140766/|archive-date=2021-03-12}}</ref>

